## Collection Caching

### Basic Collection Cache

```erb
<!-- Automatically caches each article individually -->
<%= render partial: 'articles/article', 
           collection: @articles, 
           cached: true %>
```

### Custom Cache Key

```erb
<!-- Include version in cache key -->
<%= render partial: 'articles/article',
           collection: @articles,
           cached: ->(article) { [article, 'v2'] } %>

<!-- Include current user in cache key -->
<%= render partial: 'articles/article',
           collection: @articles,
           cached: ->(article) { [article, Current.user] } %>
```

### Performance Optimization

```ruby
# In controller - preload data to avoid N+1
def index
  @articles = Article.published
                     .includes(:user, :category, :tags)
                     .recent
                     .limit(20)
end
```

